</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">在上次的<strong>克雷西战役</strong>大胜之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国士气爆棚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本想趁热一锅端下法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可谁也没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战斗指数<strong>SSS级</strong>的<strong>黑死病</strong>说来就来——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以一人感染全市丢命的超强杀伤力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">横扫整个欧洲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/2cec38c3108746f7b581c2528b1514b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下人命都保不住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还打什么仗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百年战争不得不按下暂停键</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一停</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十年就过去了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/63947dd0bc2e4b8c9a64eb2635b88e8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这十年里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国的<strong>爱德华三世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熬死了法国<strong>腓力</strong>牛排<strong>六世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等到了<strong>约翰二世</strong>上任了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于英国来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这倒算是件好事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟约翰二世人送外号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好人约翰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/5edaee5c08fb476f9d0868f09e31567b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约翰二世上位的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好对上黑死病</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果好不容易熬完了黑死病</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爱德华三世</strong>就立马来搞事情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继续用着远程熘近战的老招数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来打法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/f77fa2f9a3e7454298540aaca1fa556d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在1356年的<strong>普瓦捷之战</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国又把法国打得嗷嗷叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还顺带把约翰二世给<strong>绑回家了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逼得法国签下<strong>《布勒丁尼和约》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要求给大量的土地和金钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才肯放人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/ea53e6d06488428d9785a8327f1f0103.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后面法国提出交换人质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以把儿子抵在英国为交换</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让约翰二世回国筹钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/8b5d9348b10a4838acfd77c63ffbc2cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约翰确实没鸽人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是法国<strong>经济不景气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人民还不堪重负到处起义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这钱到期了也没能筹够</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为人质的儿子等不及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定<strong>先鸽为上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是便从英国偷偷熘跑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按常理说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样约翰二世不就可以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接不还钱在法国苟着了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/1532135c2eb648f587ef0593d399c6c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约翰二世表示拒绝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为国王且是骑士的他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有着自己的追求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就算儿子跑了钱也没筹够</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>骑士精神也永不磨灭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我要自己回去蹲监狱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蹲回自己的尊严</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/665c3e005a6c47ba92fb5b70d50dc626.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但法国人没料到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国王这一蹲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接在监狱蹲到<strong>人没了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而英国人也没料到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约翰二世这一死</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己的好日子开始进入<strong>倒计时模式</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为百年战争开打以来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国最靠谱的一届国王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">终于上位了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他就是约翰二世的儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>查理五世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/530efe69b542447ab6f5327c3cd4d9cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/3a3ede29c75e43dfb1c732d000041840.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理五世上位后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>改编军队、整顿税制、加强王权</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最重要的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国还在<strong>原地踏步</strong>为自己的长弓沾沾自喜时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理五世已经开始鼓捣起<strong>火炮</strong>来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/2a8434222dee4deeaf2a73e4779590b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1369年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一直被动的法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主动向英国开战</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/cb2c50a3a7e741e1b1c1f9b4eece6119.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实话说回来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国一直用的长弓兵战术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>并不是预先设计好</strong>专门针对法国的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一切都是个美丽意外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/ab567a6c8ae340e29c2a95d644f06253.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国国王和贵族之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">算是<strong>“以物换物”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>国王提供地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贵族负责打仗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以那时候的贵族</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是<strong>通过打仗来区分自己和平民</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/b803d491eb5544ec940ab4e05531225c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随着经济的发展</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>货币</strong>逐渐出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且经济模式从<strong>谷物生产</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">转化成了<strong>生产经济作物和发展畜牧业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贵族更想去学<strong>母猪的产后护理</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而不是浪费时间接受骑士训练</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是便出现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>给钱代替服军役</strong>的方法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/039ccc9d1fcf42889629d9c223be39d9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>议会</strong>的出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">制约国王维护自身利益</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保障了贵族的权益</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等到了打仗的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国王发现自己王权掌控度不足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贵族却有议会撑腰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且按规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贵族一年服军役40天就行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4add4b51875b40188371f69468cd76bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战一打起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁也没办法保证40天就能结束</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然国王可以叫他们继续服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但贵族也有拒绝的权利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就导致英国骑士军团不足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这才招募了一堆<strong>平民</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来做弓箭手来凑数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/21b8ba87611e4df9bb78955b815e7f5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁没想到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长弓兵的出现反而成了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>英国最有利的武器</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/af08db96ff5e4efda0fd6890043e6173.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长弓兵的运用也是<strong>有条件的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟是玩阴的那套</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然得挑选<strong>有障碍物的地点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进行战术部署</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掩护之后在暗处<strong>biubiubiu</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果没有大片<strong>丛林河流</strong>之类的掩护</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英军就得把随身携带的<strong>木桩</strong>立在阵前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提前部署以防骑士的冲锋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/dd5b4b74320a41a288da8348163ec33c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过几次战役的法军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然也不是白打的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在查理五世的指导下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国舍弃了骑兵列队冲锋的死板招数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以更灵活的招式袭击、骚扰英军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>让他们的箭雨战术没办法施行</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以此大败英军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把他们赶到了沿海边缘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">收复了大量土地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/b48df741206a4f608c619dfac6c727dd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼瞅着自个儿要失去所有领地了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国决定暂停进度条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1396年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双方缔结了二十年停战协定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百年战争第二阶段完结</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/ff13c07bace9448ba69a44c222b8856f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/847e8d73145049aeb87d9684c5597a71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这二十年里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国的查理五世去世了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">查理六世继承父业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却给了英国一个打翻身仗的机会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为查理六世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有精神病</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是法国国内两派</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>奥尔良派</strong>以及<strong>勃艮第派</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始为了争夺摄政权搞内讧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">混战不止</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/6fa387648fa7469490a5757c60d7465b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而查理五世之前打仗打得勐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花钱更是花得勐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搞得<strong>民不聊生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">农民起义不断 市民暴动不止</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在他死后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所有矛盾一齐爆发出来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致法国乱成了一锅粥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到此情此景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隔壁刚上位的英国国王</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亨利五世</strong>笑开了花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/002303789e69455284c8ae2519217e45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/b837512935b64314902af42ac6c56c69.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然二十年约期未满</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但这波机会不能错过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>1415年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亨利五世领兵进攻法国</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重启<strong>百年战争</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然这次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英军人数依旧占下风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看起来似乎不占优势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/c422803e43fc4f368d941242c0931972.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在法国搞内讧两派中的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勃艮第派<strong>公然勾结英军</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国这边只要搞定奥尔良派就好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">障碍小了很多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是在<strong>阿金库尔战役</strong>中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国长弓兵重新发挥优势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最终以英军伤亡百来人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>法军伤亡上万人的结果</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又一次以少胜多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大败法军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>甚至还把奥尔良派的大佬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和查理六世都给俘虏了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/295fe27d05fb4a728ded75883d322b8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/050388439b5247c58157aa966e9226f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于大佬们被俘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国家乱成一团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>短短五年内</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>法国地盘也被英国占去一大半</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这仗别说打赢了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保法国不成为英国的一个市都难</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没办法只好认怂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是1420年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">法国被迫签署毫无尊严的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《特鲁瓦条约》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">条约中规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>英国国王亨利五世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成为法国摄政王</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>并且在查理六世去世后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拥有继承法国王位的权利</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简而言之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此时的法国差不多就相当于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英国的一个市这样的待遇了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/aa7dc4a4a53a4d16a9e39c4ca75a0c81.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁也没想到的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亨利五世和查理六世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">居然在同一年去世了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然按照条约</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亨利六世</strong>可以直接继承法国王位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但法国这边的<strong>查理七世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不想轻易放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下英法两边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又开始为王位开始各自较劲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/d29d9b4d5ac54de1bbdf2e43ba32243f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要说最难的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还属法国老百姓们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们被入侵的英国疯狂压榨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各项掠夺、税收</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都压得他们喘不过气来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而查理七世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却依旧被英国力压一截</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后被包围在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通往法国南方的要塞<strong>奥尔良城</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里一旦失守</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那法国算是真的要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凉了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/7801f5ef7c8743628dbc26b584c13ad2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就在这个时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个<strong>法国平民女性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">敲响了城堡大门</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她的出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将拉开百年战争<strong>第四阶段序幕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于她做了什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们<strong>下次继续</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/dfe371649a904493aacf6838c73597a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/2d82bffadf6f44ee8deb27ef88abae73.png" max-width="600" /></p>
